<h1>Howzit Kiki!</h1>
<h2><%= @subscription.user.first_name %> was sent this (to <%= @subscription.user.email %>):</h2>
<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #1f4632; padding: 2rem;">
  <h1 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Hi <%= @subscription.user.first_name %>! 👋</h1>
  <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
    Your subscription (which started on <strong><%= @subscription.start_date.strftime('%e %b %Y') %></strong>) has run its course.
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
    Over this time, we've collected <strong><%= @subscription.collections.where(skip: false).count %> times</strong>
    and picked up a total of <strong><%= @subscription.XL? ? @subscription.collections.where(skip: false).sum(:buckets) : @subscription.collections.where(skip: false).sum(:bags) %> <%= @subscription.XL? ? "buckets" : "bags" %></strong> of compostables! ♻️
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
    We've loved collecting your <strong>gooi-goodies</strong> — every bit of organic waste you diverted helped feed the soil and reduce landfill pressure.
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
    <strong>Thank you for resubscribing!</strong> 🎉 We're so glad you're continuing your gooiing journey with us.
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
    Hope you are enjoying the service. Please feel free to leave a review on the
    <a href="https://www.gooi.me/testimonials/new" style="color: #1f4632;">gooi page</a>
    or on
    <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/gooi:+compost+collections/@-34.0259415,18.441836,11z/data=!4m8!3m7!1s0x4787be6c2d5d66a3:0x8d03ec96399208ea!8m2!3d-34.0259416!4d18.441836!9m1!1b1!16s%2Fg%2F11vpylc5y0?entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI2MDUxMC4wIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D" style="color: #1f4632;">google</a>
    to help spread our impact.
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
    See you soon (and your kitchen scraps too) 👀🍌🥬
  </p>
  <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">Thanks again,</p>
  <p>
    Kristen
    <%#= image_tag 'email-signature.png', alt: "Kristen Kennedy email signature", style: "max-width: 250px; margin-top: 10px;" %>
  </p>
  <%= image_tag image_url('email-signature.png'), alt: "Kristen Kennedy email signature", style: "max-width: 250px; margin-top: 10px;" %>

</div>
